Package com.stremebase.dal

com.stremebase.dal is the Data Access Layer (along with the fields).

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cursor
    Cursor is the result of a database query
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cursor.BasicCursor
    The normal not-bigData -cursor, used when search result fits into main memory
    Cursor.StreamCursor
    The big data cursor that will not store search results and therefore allows only forward iteration and does not support sorting
    Cursor.TopNCursor
    The big data cursor that supports sorting by keeping only Top (according to sortOrder) N (defined by limit) search results
    Field<T>
    The abstract base class for fields.
    KeySpace
    Shares the Long.MAX_VALUE key space between tables with even-sized partitions so that relations and search results can contain separable keys from multiple tables
    KeySpace.SharedKey
    The shared key class
    Table
    Table is container for all fields that share common key (belong to the same database entity).
    TableRelation
    Relates keys from two tables.
    Value
    Highest level methods for reading and writing data to database.

Package com.stremebase.dal Description

com.stremebase.dal is the Data Access Layer (along with the fields). Hides all implementation details.
